| `?page=2&limit=10` | `slice(10,20)` → 5 remaining items |
| `?limit=5` | `slice(0,5)` → 5 items; `ceil(15/5)=3` total pages |
| `?page=100` (out of range) | `slice(990,1000)` → `[]` naturally, no special-case needed |

